{"tid":216662,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去旅行訓街好失禮咩","createTime":"2017-04-25T10:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T07:42:56.000Z","uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39425c7f1cbe0d07a1aab022992275434d372d20","tid":216662,"uid":44509,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"之前係四國，去度一個叫宿毛既地方<br />\n睇下鬥牛，釣下魚。到左夜晚番去JR 車站訓。<br />\n<br />\n朋友聽完，就話去旅行要去到要訓街，不如唔好去啦<br />\n心諗，係唔係要玩玩食食住好先叫旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0890b39024b24284a1e1a8a28400326c9fc5738b","tid":216662,"uid":28184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"咁每個人旅行嘅理由同埋目的都唔一樣<br />\n自己開心咪得囉洗撚理人點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4774332da8d71fcbb1d9abfde1b45714c49f577d","tid":216662,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"其實算係一種體驗<br />\n好似你去歐洲咁<br />\n大把backpackers 瞓車站公園<br />\n不過日本好似冇乜人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261e633d747e3116ca02e2ae12f5fc6278886c3c","tid":216662,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你鐘意的話其實無問題"},{"pid":"0366e0d2e092839c3e739833ca36a6bec5228df3","tid":216662,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"你想係邊訓係你嘅自由<br />\n其他人冇權反對你<br />\n但亦無義務同意或支持你喎<br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得正常"},{"pid":"080e2b9df6bd79136f6f860fa998b3ba2dc557cd","tid":216662,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"自己開心咪得"},{"pid":"6a2ba3c485f6865fca69d95e87d25e5b0455d338","tid":216662,"uid":22824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:04:41.000Z","